        "class": "",
        "text": ") to deliver to them from his own mouth what he had written. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Moses spake in the ears of all the congregation — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Pronounced himself, with an audible voice, to the representatives of the congregation, and afterward ordered to be repeated to the people of every tribe, the following song or hymn.",
